OL,6,FHe believes something needs to be done
OL,7,Furgently about the water quality of
OL,8,Fthe river.
OL,10,FMark said: "I feel we're at a tipping
OL,11,Fpoint with the rivers where any users
OL,12,Fwhether they're anglers, paddle
OL,13,Fboarders or dog walkers, could fall
OL,14,Fill enough to die."
OL,16,FMark Erdwin spent several hours
OL,17,Fcasting from the river bank that day,
OL,18,Fwhen he decided to take a break.
