OL,6,FA spokesperson for Thames Water said:
OL,7,F"The health of our rivers is affected
OL,8,Fby many factors, including industry,
OL,9,Fwildlife, runoff from roads and farms,
OL,10,Fand discharges from sewage systems.
OL,11,FEveryone has a critical role to play.
OL,13,F"Government advice is that rivers and
OL,14,Fother open water locations that are
OL,15,Fnot designated as bathing waters are
OL,16,Fmanaged for the purpose of protecting
OL,17,Ffish and wildlife, not people, so
OL,18,Fhealth risks from using these
OL,19,Flocations may be higher than at
OL,20,Fdesignated bathing waters."
