OL,6,F"Our EDM Map is available to help
OL,7,Fmembers of the public make informed
OL,8,Fdecisions. We were the first water
OL,9,Fcompany to publish real time data on
OL,10,Four website, which in its first year
OL,11,Fhas been viewed over 350,000 times."
OL,13,FThe quality of the water in rivers in
OL,14,Fthe Thames Valley is once again in the
OL,15,Fspotlight as rowers from around the
OL,16,Fworld descend on Henley for the Royal
OL,17,FRegatta in July.
OL,19,FThousands of rowers will be descending
OL,20,Fon the town, with more than thirty
OL,21,Fcrews coming from overseas.
